            <p class="comment-content">深夜看这本书，恰好喜欢的人刚被骗了，不免有点悲凉，想说一句话，学计谋不是为了钱害别人，只是希望可以护自己和所爱的人周全。就像那句话说的，知世故而不世故，做一个奸的好人</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1040843891">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1040843891" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1040843891" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1040843891">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Eliparvic/">Eliparvic</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">奸者祸国、忠者祸身……</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

